claim.claim-text:
1. A magnetometer assembly comprising:
a first inner coil and a second inner coil disposed about a common axis and separated axially;
a first outer coil disposed concentrically about the first inner coil and a second outer coil disposed concentrically about the second inner coil;
a first plurality of magnetically saturable wires disposed parallel to the common axis between the first inner coil and the first outer coil; and
a second plurality of magnetically saturable wires disposed parallel to the common axis between the second inner coil and the second outer coil.
